{
  "stem": "13981.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I forget the exact time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they-- when they came back, they told me confidentially that they had been put into military camp for learning to shoot pistols, rifles, and machine guns at the age of about 16.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] The teachers, by the way, that I had did not show any anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, as I said, the kids treated me fairly well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I got along fine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the teachers, as I mentioned already-- they [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] didn't show any particular anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, never did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I heard many of his speeches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, here's the thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, Germany had just lived through terrible inflation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[COUGHS] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of us thought that once Hitler could stabilize the economical situation that they would-- that he would relent on his anti-Semitism, but that didn't happen, of course.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And talking about inflation, I remember one particular incident.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, I still have the coin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Around 1923, my brother asked my mother to give him some money to buy a lollipop.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother gave him 5 million marks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he came back crying from the grocery store across the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He couldn't buy a lollipop for 5 million marks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, if it were nowadays, it would be $1,400,000.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He couldn't buy a lollipop for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The mark-- German money was worthless.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A shirt, I read someplace, cost-- I don't-- millions and millions of marks, a plain old shirt.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm told-- now, I didn't see this, or at least I don't recall it-- that people went and got their wages, got their payment, and went to the banks [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] having wheat barrels to hold their money.",
      "word_count": 41
    }
  ],
